title: Neff North Vs. South:  Tactics
description: Tactics opened as a garage shop on the wrong side of the tracks in the fall of 1999. Now recognized as a powerhouse in Eugene, Oregon's business sector, this grassroots skate company has made a respectable name for themselves. After watching this video you'll see that the shop continues to manufacture homegrown raw skateboarders.
